**Push 1 (Heavy):**
Bench 4×4-6, OHP 4×6-8, Dips 3×6-8, Lateral Raise 3×10-12, Close Grip Bench 3×8-10

**Push 2 (Light):**
Incline DB 4×10-12, Machine Press 3×12-15, Cable Flye 3×12-15, Lateral Raise 4×15-20, Tricep Pushdown 3×12-15

