- Getting sick often
- Joints aching

**If You Can't Recover:**
- Drop to Upper/Lower (4 days)
- Sleep more
- Eat more
- Add deload weeks more often

**Deload Protocol:**
- Every 4-6 weeks (more frequent than other splits)
- 50% weight, same exercises
- Don't skip deloads`,
